summary: The code lists required Python packages for the project: Torch (deep learning library), Einops (tensor operations library), EfficientNet PyTorch (pre-trained deep learning model), Torchvision (computer vision tools), and Pytest (testing framework). ZetaScale is also needed at version 0.8.3.
